ygData.subject: Re: Where are the file molds
ygData.msgSnippet: File molds are available from a shopkeeper at the east end of West Karana, near Qeynos.  I forget his name.  Also available in Freeport. Not sure where else.
ygData.messageBody:
File molds are available from a shopkeeper at the east end of West
Karana, near Qeynos. I forget his name. Also available in Freeport.
Not sure where else.

Hicks
